issue.name: Vulnerable Telerik Web UI version found
issue.issueDetail:
Telerik Web UI version 2012.2.607 suffers from a cryptographic weakness which could allow unauthenticated remote attacker to defeat the cryptographic protection mechanism, leading to the disclosure of encryption key and discovery of the encrypted link used to access the Document Manager page, where arbitrary files could be uploaded.

See CVE-2017-9248 for further information.
